 />\n搵埋d垃圾公司</blockquote><br />\n呢個好似唔係政府project黎？"},{"pid":"edb1958fda1901ee954928e998ab70e4c3a4a13e","tid":212003,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T06:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a962b795526ec4d98a2cabef192c83dfdd6d2f2d","tid":212003,"uid":48442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T07:02:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5a66b6c48ab3993855684c7a593d3b5576c0cdc","tid":212003,"uid":68285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T07:05:22.000Z","msg":"信用卡其實有儲值卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e44119e11f6b97a23a54e833c8f888949303e9","tid":212003,"uid":64426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T07:06:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>http傳送credit card資料係好離譜<br />\n中學雞都唔會犯咁既錯</blockquote><br />\nAgger<br />\n間公司連啲基本control measures都未做好<br />\n仲好意思屌鳩人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老老柒柒<br />\n出去買張真ssl cert都係幾千蚊3年<br />\n而家乜柒web service都一定有埋https<br />\n咁都唔做<br />\n呢間公司IT真係小學雞都不如</blockquote><br />\n判左比大陸佬做係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effd7a1083b18f8685f5034eeaad5df7665cefbc","tid":212003,"uid":430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T07:06:44.000Z","msg":"連PCI compliance 最基本嘅HTTPS都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3256778c1cb4fbf06785077d6b0e7cd7853208","tid":212003,"uid":48442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T07:34:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4de237f6a726c3388f6168428e691b4c73384322","tid":212003,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T08:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係真用http send credit card data<br />\n真係要cut卡<br />\n連小學雞求其上網download個network sniffer都撈到data</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f17174a79801acdb435bca7a2c738acea84e00","tid":212003,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T09:01:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4161f80694410fe437ac072469adf63c50405e77","tid":212003,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T09:17:35.000Z","msg":"共享單車變共享信用卡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好笑係單嘢冇乜人理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68955186e1e9e67ae673039b604a5bce260a715","tid":212003,"uid":1069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T09:25:53.000Z","msg":"個app 有簡體debug message <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國頂尖人才開發係咁上下"},{"pid":"fd687fbb7cd4783e50e43719b1cd24d2f1d7c07f","tid":212003,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T09:29:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個app 有簡體debug message <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國頂尖人才開發係咁上下</blockquote><br />\n平就係咁，成個公司冇諗過有私隱問題都唔出奇"}]}